OL,3,CTeachers get new guidance as ministers
OL,4,C'ban' mobile phones in schools
OL,6,FMinisters have moved ahead with a
OL,7,Fpledge to ban mobile phones in
OL,8,Fschools, publishing guidance the
OL,9,FDepartment for Education said would
OL,10,Fensure consistency in classrooms
OL,11,Facross England.
OL,13,FThe new guidance was hailed as a
OL,14,Fsignificant step by Education
OL,15,FSecretary Gillian Keegan, who
OL,16,Foriginally pledged to bring forward
OL,17,Fchanges prohibiting mobile phone use
OL,18,Fin schools at last October's Tory
OL,19,Fconference.
