OL,3,CTeachers get new guidance as ministers
OL,4,C'ban' mobile phones in schools
OL,6,FIn a statement, she said: "Schools are
OL,7,Fplaces for children to learn and
OL,8,Fmobile phones are, at a minimum, an
OL,9,Funwanted distraction in the classroom.
OL,11,F"We are giving our hard-working
OL,12,Fteachers the tools to take action to
OL,13,Fhelp improve behaviour and to allow
OL,14,Fthem to do what they do best ` teach."
