OL,3,CTeachers get new guidance as ministers
OL,4,C'ban' mobile phones in schools
OL,6,FThe Government pointed to recent
OL,7,Fofficial data that showed 29% of
OL,8,Fsecondary school pupils reported
OL,9,Fmobile phones being used when not
OL,10,Fsupposed to.
OL,12,FBut the Association of School and
OL,13,FCollege Leaders said it did not expect
OL,14,Fthe new guidance to make any
OL,15,Fdiscernible impact.
OL,17,FGeneral Secretary Geoff Barton said
OL,18,Fthat the "compulsive use" of devices
OL,19,Fwas not happening in schools but
OL,20,F"while children are out of school".
